    <fr:title text="Exponentiable arrow">Exponentiable arrow</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>A <fr:link href="jms-0033.xml" title="Carrable map" addr="jms-0033" type="local">carrable map</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{E}\xrightarrow {{p}}{B}]]></fr:tex> in a category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex> is said to be <fr:em>exponentiable</fr:em> when it is <fr:link href="jms-0032.xml" title="Exponentiable object" addr="jms-0032" type="local">exponentiable</fr:link> when viewed as an object of the slice category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathcal {C}}_{/B}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
